S&R (Support & Resistance)
Support- Below CMP, strong buying, target for short trade
Resistance- Above CMP, strong selling, target for long trade

Drawing S&R level: 
1. load 3-6 months of data pts for short trade & 12-18 months of data pts for long trade
2. identify price action zones (min 3) where price hesitated to move up/down after a brief up/down or during sharp reversals
3. fit a horizontal line on these data pts well spaces in time

based on the logic of "History repeats itself"
